{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01GpaWMYn98xfJhSv1VWhPPP","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"I need to update the existing test file to use the new `compute_step1` signature and add the strain-rate tests. Let me first check what's needed for the GRANULAR behavior class packed_info value:\n\nLooking at common.cuh: `MAKE_PACKED(mat, beh)` = `((mat) & 0xFF) | (((beh) & 0x3) << 8)`. GRANULAR = 1, so for material 2 (SAND) with GRANULAR behavior: `MAKE_PACKED(2, 1)` = `2 | (1 << 8)` = `2 | 256` = `258`.\n\nFLUID = 0, so for material 5 (WATER) with FLUID behavior: `MAKE_PACKED(5, 0)` = `5 | 0` = `5`.\n\nNow let me rewrite the test file:"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":460,"cache_read_input_tokens":97384,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":460},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"eb47956f-dbff-4960-8452-8e302b089f1c","uuid":"35d3d28d-2de5-4192-aeb8-cb844755fe23"}
